        "subject": "LU-19249 osd-zfs: support kernel v6.16",
        "message": "LU-19249 osd-zfs: support kernel v6.16\n\npage->index was renamed to page->__folio_index. Remove the\nsingle usage of page->index in osd-zfs to avoid a compilation\nfailure.\n\nTest-Parameters: trivial fstype=zfs\nSigned-off-by: Timothy Day <timday@thelustrecollective.com>\nChange-Id: I25e6b81e6cdabda9dd51c97e30c8effa77f332fc\nReviewed-on: https://review.whamcloud.com/c/fs/lustre-release/+/65188\nTested-by: Maloo <maloo@whamcloud.com>\nReviewed-by: Alex Zhuravlev <bzzz@whamcloud.com>\nTested-by: jenkins <devops@whamcloud.com>\nReviewed-by: Oleg Drokin <green@whamcloud.com>\nReviewed-by: Shaun Tancheff <shaun.tancheff@hpe.com>\n"
